        </div>


<p>Regular expression matching all possible prompts for a specific target type.
<code class="inline">regexp</code> must not have any groups, that is, when matching, <a href="../../../../lib/stdlib/doc/html/re.html#run/3"><code class="inline">re:run/3</code></a> (in
STDLIB) must return a list with one single element.</p>
