  <section class="docstring">


        <div class="specs">
          <h4 class="specs-title">Types</h4>

            <pre translate="no">Connection = <a href="#t:connection/0">connection</a>()</pre>

            <pre translate="no">CmdFormat = <a href="../../../../lib/stdlib/doc/html/io.html#t:format/0">io:format</a>()</pre>

            <pre translate="no">Args = [<a href="../../../../lib/../erts/doc/html/erlang.html#t:term/0">term</a>()]</pre>

            <pre translate="no">Opts = [{timeout, Timeout} | <a href="#t:newline_option/0">newline_option</a>()] | Timeout</pre>

            <pre translate="no">Result = {ok, Data} | {error, Reason}</pre>

            <pre translate="no">Reason = <a href="../../../../lib/../erts/doc/html/erlang.html#t:term/0">term</a>()</pre>

            <pre translate="no">Data = <a href="../../../../lib/../erts/doc/html/erlang.html#t:string/0">string</a>()</pre>

            <pre translate="no">Timeout = <a href="../../../../lib/../erts/doc/html/erlang.html#t:integer/0">integer</a>()</pre>

        </div>


<p>Sends a Telnet command and waits for prompt (uses a format string and a list of
arguments to build the command).</p><p>For details, see <a href="#cmd/3"><code class="inline">ct_telnet:cmd/3</code></a>.</p>
  </section>
